%
% This is the document format I use for just about everything. Primarily, I just
% use nicer fonts that the dreadful default, Computer Modern. In particular,
%
%  Roman       :  Sabon
%  Sans-Serif  :  Helvetic Neue
%  Math        :  Computer Modern Bright
%  Monospace   :  DejaVu Sans Mono
%
%
% I also tweak the geometry and section styles, etc.
%
%


